aS"18k Yellow Gold Filled Smooth Charming Women Earrings Wedding Hoop Jewelry HotClick to EnlargeClick to EnlargeClick to Enlarge\xc2\xa0Material18K Yellow Gold FilledSize13MM * 5MM \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 (conversion: \xc2\xa01 inch = 25.4mm or 1mm = 0.0393 inch)Retail Price$18Package included1Pair Weight3g\xc2\xa0Kindly note:\xc2\xa0\xc2\xa0\xc2\xa0The Real Item color which you receive maybe vary from the listing picture because of different Camera lens, and different light environment.\xc2\xa0Item Measure by hand, it could \xc2\xa0be \xc2\xa0a little different.What is gold filled ?\xc2\xa0Gold Filled Jewelry is a thick (about 25mil) solid layer of quality gold heat bonded onto an internal semi-precious metals by advanced mechanical process. It has all the great characteristics of solid gold jewelry without price tag . Please do not compare gold filled jewelry to plated jewelry (usually only 3 mil layer) as there is no comparison, gold filled is much more valuable and tarnish resistant than plated. It does not flake off, tarnish or discolor. It is extremely long lasting and if taken care of will last you a lifetime. Gold filled jewelry is an economical alternative to solid gold jewelry! Although it isn\xe2\x80\x99t solid gold jewelry.\xc2\xa0What causes gold to be different colors ?\xc2\xa0While pure gold is a warm yellow, it can be manufactured in a wide variety of colors-including pink, white, green, blue or gray-by being mixed with different metals. For example, when silver and copper are added to pure gold, it turns yellow. When nickel or palladium (or zinc and copper) are added, gold turns white. Pure gold combined with silver, copper and zinc results in green gold. And pink gold is made when copper is mixed with pure gold.\xc2\xa0What is the best way to care for the gold filled jewelry ?\xc2\xa0\xc2\xa0Do not wear your jewelry in hot tubs and swimming pools. Take jewelry off when using laundry or cleaning products. NEVER, NEVER clean it with bleach.Use jewelry cleaner and a soft cloth to clean your gold filled jewelry .If you do not have jewelry cleaner, you can use mild soap and warm water. Never use any harsh cleaners such as bleach or abrasives. \xc2\xa0To store gold filled jewelry, wrap each piece separately in a soft cloth. Lay herringbone chains flat so they do not kink. Always remember to remove your jewelry before sleeping, bathing or exercising.Return Policy:\xc2\xa0\xc2\xa0We accept returns within 30 days you are received the item, Buyer pay shipping fee.In case you received a wrong item, Items must be returned in its original and unused condition & must also be in its original box and packing.We do not allow refunds or exchanges because of change of mind. aS'Coins and paper money have served as the primary method of payment for centuries. The arrival of high-tech cards caused a rapid replacement of these traditional means of payment. This new era of technology calls for an innovative type of wallet. One that protects both your privacy and your money. The Secrid wallet does exactly that both in terms of security and style. The Cardprotector is the core of the Secrid product line. The aluminium Cardprotector protects your most important cards, both against bending and breaking and against your RFID cards being scanned if you don\'t want them to be (such as the transportation pass, ID card, the latest credit cards and business cards). The Cardslide is the latest product in the Secrid collection and adds just that little bit more space to the Cardprotector - for example for cash, business cards, parking tickets, a key or a nice photo in the transparent version. Some cards have thickened letters, this is called embossing. You can store up to six cards in the Cardprotector, including one with embossing. Or up to five cards, three of which with embossing. Designed and manufactured to the highest standards in the Netherlands, each Secrid product comes with a two year guarantee. aS"DescriptionIntroduce:Healthy skin should be around ph 4.5 - 6.5.Bacteria actively grow under high ph therefore we need the skin care product that can balance the ph for us.Sebum contains Fatty Acid and our sweat contains Lactic Acid,therefore oily skin = lower phdry skin = higher ph.Konjac sponge is about ph 6.2 which is close to the ph of Milk.The konjac sponge is made from a natural food material which is called Konjac(in Japan it's known as Konnyaku).Konjac is a perennial herb in aroid family and since ancient times, it has been widely used as a medical and edible natural plant.Konjac is a popular and healthy vegetable in Korea and Japan. Being unbelievably soft and gentle, konjac sponge exfoliates dead cells while wiping the face and body, and leaves behind a colloid film to nourish and protect your skin.A Konjac Sponge contains no preservatives or artificial pigment.It's perfect for cleansing even the most sensitive skin!This Facial Cleansing Sponge absorbs water well.
